msgctxt "QL_Get_MasterSword_Desc"
msgid ""
"Through the Lost Woods and deep within the\n"
"Korok Forest sleeps the <1.se_co>sword that seals the\n"
"darkness<2.re_co>, a weapon said to be capable of\n"
"striking down the Calamity.\n"
"\n"
"Though you came to claim the sword, the \n"
"Deku Tree told you the blade would test you...\n"
"Although you wielded it 100 years ago, can\n"
"you pull the sword out in your current state?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_Get_MasterSword_Finish"
msgid ""
"You've acquired the legendary <1.se_co>Master Sword<2.re_co>,\n"
"that which seals the darkness. You feel that the\n"
"sword itself delights to be in your possession...\n"
"\n"
"Even at this moment, Princess Zelda is within\n"
"Hyrule Castle, fighting to suppress the Calamity.\n"
"She endures, believing you will come for her...\n"
"\n"
"Will you be able to save her as you are now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Get_MasterSword_Name"
msgid "The Hero's Sword"
msgstr ""

